<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zse.93.10039.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Emarginula harmilensis Sturany, 1903, Station 143 (Harmil Island, Dahlak Archipelago, Eritrea, Red Sea). A-F, H. Holotype, NHMW 84290: top (A-B), aperture (C), left side (D-E), protoconch (F), microsculpture (H). G. Original figure by Sturany (1903). Scale bars: A-E: 1 mm, F: 0.1 mm, H: 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/118636" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

